game.name: Frozen Anna Baby Birth
game.description:
The day has come Anna and his love Kristoff were waiting for long. Yes, Anna is ready to deliver a baby while lying on the hospital bed. It is an amazing time as the Frozen royal family is about to grow after a few hours. She has rushed to the hospital in a hurry so the princess has only a few essentials along with a support of her husand who is waiting outside the room. You are playing the role of her medical physician in Frozen Anna Baby Birth game. 

Your favorite princess Anna looks pretty nervous, so first try to do all the things that could keep her relax. Start this brand new doctor game with examining the belly of your cute pregnant Anna! All the medical tools are available on the left and right side of the screen. So, collect them one by one to complete her health checkup and help the lady to bring her baby princess into this world. Follow the instructions to take care of the princess and her baby perfectly in this html5 surgical game!

After the birth of her baby, your job will not be finished. You also have to take care of her baby who needs the special attention. Take her blood, and use the instrument to check her heartbeat, and, calm her down with an injection! Fulfill the tasks step by step with the help of instructions shown on the screen in this html5 caring game! We are happy to bring you new doctor games time to time, so there are no possibilities of getting bored when you stay tuned with us.
